common_issues.title: Unable to cancel LLLM download on Windows Desktop Application
common_issues.description: Users are reporting an inability to stop or cancel the download of an LLLM within the latest version of the Windows desktop application.  A screenshot depicts a stuck download with an unresponsive cancel button.  Further investigation is needed to determine the root cause and provide a solution.
